  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "A ***call to action*** (CTA) is the instruction that tells the reader what to do next — the button, the link, the sentence that converts attention into action. \"Start your free trial.\" \"Download the guide.\" \"Book a consultation.\" The CTA is where the copy's persuasive work either pays off or doesn't.",
